- ✅ `IEquatable<DataSize>` implemented correctly on struct — avoids boxing
- ✅ `GetHashCode()` delegates to `long.GetHashCode()` — no allocation
- ✅ `TryParseWithSuffix` uses `StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase` — correct

